          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780399134135" href="/book/show/572645.Morning_Glory">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3938000-denise?shelf=hot_hero">hot_hero</a>, 
